{"tid":511669,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"聖誔短故(孤影人)","createTime":"2017-12-27T16:51:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-29T15:28:27.000Z","uid":90605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"31f68ef8df6004ce7b6ad27753527dc69cd70ee8","tid":511669,"uid":90605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T16:51:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">小弟文章麻麻</span><br />\n<br />\n我係一個孤獨的影子。<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n每一日的晚上，我看着人們為各種事情而煩腦。<br />\n<br />\n有時侯，人們會望着自己的影子，但我們只能沉默地守護人們。<br />\n<br />\n每個人身邊都有一個影子，我們就是孤影人。<br />\n<br />\n孤影人願意聆聽人們的故事。<br />\n<br />\n無論你失戀，孤影人都會和你走過黑影的日子，尋找新一天。<br />\n<br />\n在2017年的平安夜，孤影人在尖沙咀不再感到孤獨，因為尖沙咀充滿了人情味。<br />\n<br />\n在平安夜尖沙咀的微時，孤影人不再孤單，但是總有人單身一個渡過平安夜，孤影人在他們沉默地守護，令他們在黑暗中感受到溫暖。<br />\n<br />\n謝謝你，孤影人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03d85dbbb69b6a43a9bcc8cd5a112b267d83d9f0","tid":511669,"uid":90605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T15:28:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}